cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.DL, cs.LG, cs.MM. 

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques to rectify document images and improve their readability and OCR accuracy. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which makes cs.DL (Machine Learning) and cs.LG (Learning) likely sub-categories. The paper also involves information retrieval techniques to improve OCR accuracy, which makes cs.IR (Information Retrieval) a possible sub-category. Finally, the paper involves image manipulation techniques, which makes cs.MM (Multimedia) a possible sub-category.
